#: .\TALK_Merc_Food.json
msgid ""
"Batteries, fuel, irons, medicines...All right. Munitions are the best, they "
"are preferred. I have edible things to trade. Do not think of robbing anyone"
" here. We are all armed. Anyway, Let's Trade?"
msgstr ""

#: .\TALK_Merc_Food.json
msgid ""
"Batteries, fuel, irons, medicines...All right. Munitions are the best, "
"preferred. I have edible things to trade. Do not think of robbing anyone "
"here. We are all armed. Anyway, Let's Trade?"
msgstr ""

#: .\TALK_Merc_Food.json .\TALK_Merc_Mil.json .\Talk_Merc_Ammo.json
#: .\Talk_Merc_Bro.json
msgid "Is there anything I can help with?"
msgstr ""

#: .\TALK_Merc_Food.json .\TALK_Merc_Mil.json
msgid "Let's see what you have got..."
msgstr ""

