#: .\Talk_Merc_Bro.json
msgid "bye."
msgstr ""

#: .\TALK_Merc_Food.json
msgid "Nope."
msgstr ""

#: .\TALK_Merc_Food.json .\TALK_Merc_Mil.json .\TALK_Merc_Smith.json
#: .\Talk_Merc_Ammo.json .\Talk_Merc_Bro.json .\Talk_Merc_Med.json
msgid "Got it."
msgstr ""

#: .\TALK_Merc_Mil.json
msgid ""
"Another survivor it is. I'm trading some military supplies and munitions "
"smuggled from one of the camps nearby. You wanna trade?"
msgstr ""

#: .\TALK_Merc_Mil.json .\TALK_Merc_Smith.json
msgid "No."
msgstr ""

#: .\TALK_Merc_Smith.json
msgid "Makeshift firearms, tools, armors. What do you need?"
msgstr ""

#: .\TALK_Merc_Smith.json
msgid "Do you take forging commisions?"
msgstr ""

#: .\TALK_Merc_Smith.json
msgid "Let's trade."
msgstr ""

#: .\TALK_Merc_Smith.json .\Talk_Merc_Med.json
msgid "Bye."
msgstr ""

#: .\Talk_Merc_Ammo.json
msgid ""
"Hey, you'll need some ammo to survive out there. What kind of ammo do you "
"like? You prefer hand-reloaded, or military standard?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Talk_Merc_Ammo.json .\Talk_Merc_Bro.json
msgid "I have came here to trade."
msgstr ""

#: .\Talk_Merc_Ammo.json .\Talk_Merc_Bro.json
msgid "No, thanks."
msgstr ""

#: .\Talk_Merc_Bro.json
msgid "<greet>, Where did you come from? Came here to trade?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Talk_Merc_Med.json
msgid "<greet>, I deal with diseases and drugs. Want to buy some?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Talk_Merc_Med.json
msgid "Are you a doctor? Can you treat me?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Talk_Merc_Med.json
msgid "Let's see what you got..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Talk_Merc_Med.json
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, I'm not a real doctor. He died somewhat recently... I'm just "
"selling some of his possessions."
msgstr ""

#: .\Talk_Merc_guard_gate.json
msgid "Halt! Identify yourself."
msgstr ""

#: .\Talk_Merc_guard_gate.json
msgid "I'm just passing. What is this place?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Talk_Merc_guard_gate.json
msgid ""
"Another survivor? <greet>. Here is... the Settlement. And maybe the Hub of "
"caravans now. If you want to barter something, Then get in and check it out."
" Also, if you are considering to rob us... I will not recommend it. Unless "
"you are willing to take 7.62mm bullets."
msgstr ""

#: .\Talk_Merc_guard_gate.json
msgid "Got it. Thanks."
msgstr ""

